name: Magic Pocket watch 7000
description: Do you want to alter your future? do you want to prevent any regretful events that happened in your past life? Well, here is your chance! with the Magic Pocket Watch 7000 you can time travel and many more! Re-live your happiest memories, erase your most embarrassing drunken moments, split or merge any timelines, or even unlock the secrets of the beginning of time itself! With the Magic Pocket Watch 7000, we have added a new feature where you can reset time to your last check point if things ever go wrong. Come get yours now, at 1-(800)- MPW7000.
